full_desc: If Q27ii. DSEPILEP (Epilepsy/seizure disorder) is in 1-3 (recent conditon, condition in past 5 years, or lifelong condition), then UDS Form D1a, Q20. EPILEP (Epilepsy (present)) should not be blank or 0 (No Epilepsy present)
test_logic: If DSEPILEP in (1-3) and (EPILEP is blank or EPILEP=0)
